<article id="post-3425" class="post-3425 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-children category-general tag-birthday tag-dearchoochoo">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2015/03/happy-5th-birthday-choo-choo/" rel="bookmark">Happy 5th Birthday, Choo Choo</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>I&#8217;m having some serious trouble, Choo Choo. You&#8217;re five. FIVE. You&#8217;ve hit that penultimate step from wee babe to being a grade-schooler (the last, obviously, is going to Kindergarten; at least we have a few months before that).<br />
But still, <em>five</em>.<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2015/03/happy-5th-birthday-choo-choo/#more-3425" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;Happy 5th Birthday, Choo Choo&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
