<article id="post-3413" class="post-3413 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-children category-general tag-dearchoochoo">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2014/03/goodbye-my-lovely-three-year-old/" rel="bookmark">Goodbye, my lovely three year-old</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Well, Choo Choo, today I&#8217;m having a &#8220;last&#8221; moment. Today was your last full day as a three year-old. Tomorrow is your birthday. Tomorrow, you turn four.<br />
And I will miss you being three immensely. You are my last three year-old.<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2014/03/goodbye-my-lovely-three-year-old/#more-3413" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;Goodbye, my lovely three year-old&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
