<article id="post-3119" class="post-3119 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-children category-family category-general category-travel tag-british-columbia tag-dearchoochoo tag-dearmonkey tag-fairmont-hot-springs">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2012/06/vacation-2012-day-1/" rel="bookmark">Vacation 2012, Day 1</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Hey kids,<br />
You&#8217;re both sleeping right now. Soundly so. You&#8217;ve both had a big, exciting day, and I&#8217;m frankly amazed you made it as long as you did. You normally don&#8217;t pack this much into a few days, let alone a few hours.<br />
We&#8217;ll see how you do for the next few days&#8230;<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2012/06/vacation-2012-day-1/#more-3119" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;Vacation 2012, Day 1&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2012/06/vacation-2012-day-1/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2012-06-23T23:12:20-06:00">23 June 2012</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/children/" rel="category tag">Children</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/family/" rel="category tag">Family</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/travel/" rel="category tag">Travel</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/british-columbia/" rel="tag">british columbia</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/dearchoochoo/" rel="tag">DearChooChoo</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/dearmonkey/" rel="tag">DearMonkey</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/fairmont-hot-springs/" rel="tag">fairmont hot springs</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2012/06/vacation-2012-day-1/#respond">Leave a comment<span class="screen-reader-text"> on Vacation 2012, Day 1</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
