<article id="post-2721" class="post-2721 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-children category-family category-general category-travel tag-dearchoochoo tag-dearmonkey tag-manitoba tag-roadtrip tag-saskatchewan tag-winnipeg">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2010/08/the-great-family-roadtrip-2010-day-6/" rel="bookmark">The Great Family Roadtrip 2010, Day 6</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>We were all slow to rise today, but we made quick work of breakfast. You said goodbye to your Great Uncle Ken and Great Aunt Marilyn before we headed to the car. Our first stop was to drop off Granny at the airport. She wasn&#8217;t driving back with us, which I take to be a very wise decision on her part.<br />
Then we headed back down to Portage, which is one of the main roads in Winnipeg. After a stop at Timmy&#8217;s for a coffee recharge, we set our sights for Saskatchewan and our overnight stop at Moosomin.<br />
The question was what were we going to do in between&#8230;<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2010/08/the-great-family-roadtrip-2010-day-6/#more-2721" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;The Great Family Roadtrip 2010, Day 6&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2010/08/the-great-family-roadtrip-2010-day-6/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2010-08-09T21:30:08-06:00">9 August 2010</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/children/" rel="category tag">Children</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/family/" rel="category tag">Family</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/travel/" rel="category tag">Travel</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/dearchoochoo/" rel="tag">DearChooChoo</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/dearmonkey/" rel="tag">DearMonkey</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/manitoba/" rel="tag">manitoba</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/roadtrip/" rel="tag">roadtrip</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/saskatchewan/" rel="tag">saskatchewan</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/winnipeg/" rel="tag">winnipeg</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2010/08/the-great-family-roadtrip-2010-day-6/#respond">Leave a comment<span class="screen-reader-text"> on The Great Family Roadtrip 2010, Day 6</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
